xing\", \"score\": 0.9985476304289181, \"rank\": 0.001454481091368572, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"late May\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"introducinggender testingto\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"the eligibility\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"male and female athletes\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1862}, {\"ngram\": \"its competitions\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The governing body issued an apology the next week for having named Khelif in its statement about the new eligibility rules.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 2009, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The governing body\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1903}, {\"ngram\": \"an apology\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1921}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"its statement\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"the new eligibility rules\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The genetic sex test was used at the Olympics between 1968 and 1996, after which it was abandoned.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The genetic sex test\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In June, new International Olympic Committee president Kirsty Coventry said the body would set up a gender working group and vowed to take a \\\"scientific approach\\\" to the inflammatory issue of eligibility for the female categories.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2124, \"end\": 2155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"],